msgid "# ConvertTo-DnsServerPrimaryZone"
msgstr "# 将该区域转换为DNS服务器的主区域"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "Converts a zone to a DNS primary zone."
msgstr "将一个区域转换为DNS主区域。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "### ADZone (Default)"
msgstr "### ADZone（默认设置）"

msgid "### FileZone"
msgstr "### FileZone"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **ConvertTo-DnsServerPrimaryZone** cmdlet converts a Domain Name System (DNS) zone to a DNS primary zone.\n"
"Use this cmdlet to promote a secondary zone to a primary zone on the server.\n"
"For a file-backed zone, ensure there is only one server that hosts the primary zone."
msgstr ""
"`ConvertTo-DnsServerPrimaryZone` cmdlet 可将域名系统（DNS）区域转换为 DNS 主区域。使用此 cmdlet "
"可将辅助区域提升为服务器上的主区域。对于基于文件的区域，请确保只有一台服务器托管该主区域。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Convert a file-backed zone"
msgstr "#### 示例 1：转换一个基于文件的区域文件"

msgid ""
"This command converts zone named west03.contoso.com to a file-backed primary zone on the current server.\n"
"This example uses the *Force* parameter to skip a confirmation message."
msgstr ""
"此命令将名为 west03.contoso.com 的区域转换为当前服务器上的一个基于文件的主体区域（primary zone）。示例中使用了 "
"*Force* 参数来跳过确认消息。"

msgid "### Example 2: Convert an Active Directory-integrated zone"
msgstr "### 示例 2：转换一个与 Active Directory 集成的区域"

msgid ""
"This command converts a zone named west04.contoso.com to an Active Directory-integrated primary zone.\n"
"The zone will be replicated to all DNS servers in the domain.\n"
"This example uses the *Force* parameter to skip a confirmation message."
msgstr ""
"此命令将名为 west04.contoso.com 的区域转换为与 Active Directory 集成的主区域。该区域将被复制到域中的所有 DNS "
"服务器上。此示例使用了 *Force* 参数来跳过确认消息。"

